            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/8803109/">惹人爱的小老鼠</a></h2>

                <div id="review_8803109_short" class="review-short" data-rid="8803109">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        故事和讲述都是典型的美式装备，不过改换了“人物”的设置之后倒是也别有一番风味，而且制作得还相当用心，值得肯定。很童趣的电影，充满了想象力，潜移默化地植入了亲情的伟大主题。萌萌的小老鼠在童话式的呈现下令人无比爱怜。Stuart的乐观与活泼极具感染力，无法叫人不爱。...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8803109-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_8803109_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_8803109_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="8803109" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-8803109">
                                34
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="8803109" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-8803109">
                                2
                        </span>
